ScenegraphXML Scene Graph Generator Plug-in
===========================================

The Scenegraph XML Scene Graph Generator (SGG) plug-in implements the same
functionality of the ScenegraphXML node. It parses an XML file with structured
scene information and generates the scene graph accordingly.

Environment Variables
---------------------

BOOST_HOME   The root of the boost directory.
KATANA_HOME  The Katana installation directory at compile-time

Building
--------

1. Ensure the environment variables listed above have been set.
2. Run 'make'.
3. Copy 'out/ScenegraphXML.so' to the 'Libs' subdirectory within a
   Katana resources path.
